    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Simple chests constructed of six boards butted, lapped, nailed, and hinged together; an economical alternative to joined chests.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000014591/Fairbanks and Bates, American Furniture (1981)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Baúles sencillos construidos con seis tableros unidos sin traslapar, sobrepuestos, clavados y abisagrados juntos, una alternativa económica a los arcones.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Eenvoudige kisten uit zes platen die samen zijn gevoegd, gelapt, gespijkerd en van scharnieren voorzien. Ze vormen een goedkoop alternatief voor kisten van schrijnwerk.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>由六個板子連接釘在一起的簡易箱櫃；可作為組合箱櫃的簡約替代品。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
